data.title: 1967 Press Photo Johnson and Japan's Eisaku Sato talk in White House office
data.meta_description: This is an original press photo. Photo is dated 11-14-1967. It may contain wrinkles, cracks, and possibly even tears due to its age and how it was handled before it got to us. A scanner may interpret colors and contrast differently than human eyes will, so it is possible that the actual photograph may be slightly darker or lighter in person.
